Habitat data from luquillo.

Source: R/data-luquillo-other.R

Habitat data from luquillo created by dividing elevation data in multiple chunks.

luquillo_habitat

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 503 rows and 3 columns.

See also

  • luquillo_elevation.

  • https://forestgeo.si.edu/sites/north-america/luquillo.
